    "text": "Colombo Port Police Station Investigates Discovery of Unidentified Body",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      357.28,
      512.48,
      398.16
    ],
    "text": "On the morning of 9 May 2026, the Colombo Port Police Station commenced an investigation following the discovery of an unidentified body in the sea near Port of Colombo.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      412.62,
      385.75,
      425.9
    ],
    "text": "The identity of the deceased has not yet been established.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      440.46,
      521.62,
      467.54
    ],
    "text": "The individual is described as approximately 5 feet 6 inches tall, with short hair and a beard. At the time of discovery, he was wearing black shorts and a brown shirt.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      481.98,
      492.88,
      509.06
    ],
    "text": "The body has been placed in the mortuary of National Hospital of Sri Lanka for further examination.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      523.62,
      461.14,
      536.9
    ],
    "text": "Ongoing investigations are being conducted by the Colombo Port Police.",
    "fonts": [
